failed.title: You should not change or delete the existing elements in the head tag
The styles.css file should be empty
Do not use any inline styles, just use the bootstrap classes for styling
The body should contain a div tag
The div tag should contain the class container-fluid
The div tag should contain a <div> with class row
The row should contain 2 columns with 2 and 10 slots
The left column should contain a <nav> tag with anchor tags with class nav-link
The right column should contain a jumbotron with py-2 class
The jumbotron should contain an H4, a p and a button
The button in the jumbotron should be blue and medium size
